For those who say photos are too photoshopped now-a-days . Heres a before and after photo from Hurrell's Hollywood Portraits in the 1930's .
Most of the basic tools in Photoshop are actually based on things that a skilled photographer could do in a darkroom . Burning, smudging, cropping, etc.
